data.description: Welcome to 143 Pemberton Blvd, Browns Mills, NJ—an inviting property that offers both comfort and convenience. This beautiful home boasts three cozy bedrooms, one recently updated bathroom, and a spacious layout perfect for anyone looking to create a warm and welcoming living space. The living room offers ample space for entertaining guests or enjoying quiet evenings in front of the cozy, warm wood burning fireplace with loved ones. Each of the three bedrooms provides a private retreat with plenty of closet space for storage. The bathroom is well-appointed and includes modern fixtures and finishes, ensuring a fresh and functional space to start your day. The heart of the home lies in its vibrant kitchen. Perhaps the most enchanting feature of this property is the large patio situated in the expansive backyard. It's an entertainers dream, offering endless opportunities for summer BBQs, outdoor activities or simply lounging by the fire pit. All this situated just moments away from local amenities and Joint Base McGuire-Dix-Lakehurst.
